\p
\v 12 Ephraim surrounds me with lies and Israel with deceit, and Judah still wanders with some deity, faithful to some “Holy One.”\f + \fr 11:12 \ft It seems that Judah was merging ideas from pagan worship with that of the true God, and using the term “el” which was the name of the highest Canaanite god but could also be applied to Yahweh. So what is being said here seems to be that Judah too is wavering in its allegiance to the true God.\f*   
\b  
\c 12  
\p
\v 1 Ephraim tries \w to|strong="H3478"\w* herd \w the|strong="H5437"\w* wind, chasing \w after|strong="H1004"\w* \w the|strong="H5437"\w* east wind \w all|strong="H5437"\w* day \w long|strong="H5750"\w*. \w Their|strong="H5437"\w* \w lies|strong="H3585"\w* \w and|strong="H3063"\w* violence keep \w on|strong="H1004"\w* increasing. \w They|strong="H4820"\w* \w make|strong="H5437"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* treaty \w with|strong="H5973"\w* Assyria, \w and|strong="H3063"\w* send olive oil \w to|strong="H3478"\w* Egypt.\f + \fr 12:1 \ft In other words, while making a treaty with Assyria they are covering their options by trying to gain support from Egypt as well by sending supplies of olive oil. \f*  
\v 2 \w The|strong="H3605"\w* Lord \w also|strong="H3117"\w* \w has|strong="H3117"\w* \w an|strong="H3772"\w* accusation \w against|strong="H5973"\w* Judah, \w and|strong="H3117"\w* \w will|strong="H4714"\w* punish Jacob \w for|strong="H4714"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w way|strong="H3605"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* people act; \w he|strong="H3117"\w* \w will|strong="H4714"\w* repay \w them|strong="H7291"\w* \w for|strong="H4714"\w* what \w they|strong="H3117"\w* \w have|strong="H7462"\w* \w done|strong="H3605"\w*.  
\v 3 \w Even|strong="H3068"\w* \w in|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* womb \w he|strong="H3068"\w* fought \w with|strong="H5973"\w* \w his|strong="H3068"\w* brother;\f + \fr 12:3 \ft Literally, “he grasped his brother's heel.”\f* \w when|strong="H7725"\w* \w he|strong="H3068"\w* \w became|strong="H7725"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* man \w he|strong="H3068"\w* fought \w with|strong="H5973"\w* \w God|strong="H3068"\w*.  
