\v 8 Ephraim says, “\w I|strong="H3027"\w*'m rich! \w I|strong="H3027"\w*'ve made myself wealthy! \w I|strong="H3027"\w*'ve made \w so|strong="H3027"\w* \w much|strong="H3027"\w* \w from|strong="H3027"\w* \w my|strong="H3027"\w* \w work|strong="H3027"\w*, \w and|strong="H3027"\w* nobody can prove \w me|strong="H3027"\w* guilty \w of|strong="H3027"\w* \w doing|strong="H3027"\w* \w wrong|strong="H6231"\w*.”   
\p
