\b  
\c 14  
\p
\v 1 Return, Israel, \w to|strong="H5307"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* Lord \w your|strong="H3588"\w* God, \w because|strong="H3588"\w* \w your|strong="H3588"\w* sins \w have|strong="H3588"\w* brought \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w down|strong="H5307"\w*.  
