\p
\v 8 Ephraim, how much \w more|strong="H7725"\w* \w do|strong="H1612"\w* \w I|strong="H6738"\w* \w have|strong="H1612"\w* \w to|strong="H7725"\w* warn \w you|strong="H7725"\w* \w about|strong="H7725"\w* idols?\f + \fr 14:8 \ft In other words, God has had enough of the subject.\f* \w I|strong="H6738"\w* \w have|strong="H1612"\w* \w answered|strong="H7725"\w* \w and|strong="H7725"\w* now \w I|strong="H6738"\w* am watching.\f + \fr 14:8 \ft To see the people's response. \f* \w I|strong="H6738"\w* am \w like|strong="H7725"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w tree|strong="H1612"\w* \w that|strong="H7725"\w* \w is|strong="H1715"\w* evergreen; \w your|strong="H7725"\w* fruit \w is|strong="H1715"\w* found \w in|strong="H3427"\w* \w me|strong="H7725"\w*.   
